{"tid":2346403,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"電影動作指導工作室涉藏違禁武器 獲准簽保守行為結案","createTime":"2020-12-30T08:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T10:36:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"99c601f14e71713298c9af5af9a5315de3c259ff","tid":2346403,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:32:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12531\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12531&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=9df98718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12531</a><br />\n<br />\n#屯門裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#張潔宜署理主任裁判官 <br />\n#20200124觀塘<br />\n#審前覆核<br />\n<br />\n陳(52)<br />\n控罪:管有違禁武器<br />\n<br />\n案情:警方於2020年1月24日持搜查令搜查觀塘成業街一工廠大廈的單位，搜出違禁武器包括指節套、彈叉、彈叉橡筋、武士劍、雙截棍、金屬珠和塑膠珠，並拘捕被告。被告於扣留期間保持緘默。<br />\n<br />\n控辯雙方同意以簽保守行為方式處理，被告以$1000簽保守行為12個月，期間不得干犯與管有違禁武器或藏有攻擊性武器相關的罪行，否則$1000將被充公，亦須面對相關控罪的指控。<br />\n證物P2-11充公，P1及P12發還警方。<br />\n$500堂費從保釋金中扣除。✅"},{"pid":"c356cc62a5d0485b4a6d92acc795fbd6d87dc9be","tid":2346403,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"中年電影男演員兼動作指導位於觀塘的工作室早前遭警方搜查，搜出斧頭、手刺及武士刀等物品，事後被控一項管有違禁武器罪。案件今日再訊，控方表明撤銷起訴，被告准以自簽1,000元、守行為一年結案。<br />\n<br />\n被告早前被控一項管有攻擊性武器，指他於今年1月24日在觀塘成業街成業工業大廈3樓單位內，管有兩把斧頭、兩把軍刀、兩把武士刀、兩個丫叉、三條丫叉橡筋、兩包膠珠及一包鋼珠；另一項管有違禁武器罪則指他在同日同地管有三個鐵蓮花、一支雙截棍以及一個手刺。<br />\n<br />\n案情指警方今年1月24日清晨6時突擊檢查觀塘成業街成業工業大廈3樓一單位，在單位內搜出大批刀具武器，當中包括屬違禁武器的手刺。被告隨即被捕，警誡下不發一言。被告今天在屯門法院同意控方案情，獲准自簽1,000元，守行為12個月，另附堂費500元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/QEZHSPZS3NGJHLB6AVNNKUR6PY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FQEZHSPZS3NGJHLB6AVNNKUR6PY%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=3ee3425a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FQEZHSPZS3NGJHLB6AVNNKUR6PY%2F&h=1d5b9a52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/QEZHSPZS3NGJHLB6AVNNKUR6PY/</a>"},{"pid":"e191e44e192afe40e572bcf189e8d441fc8ed069","tid":2346403,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:33:55.000Z","msg":"唔夠料告夾硬留records"},{"pid":"4f63961a54a21483a99e050ac7fff514ed251513","tid":2346403,"uid":126283,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e191e44e192afe40e572bcf189e8d441fc8ed069","tid":2346403,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:33:55.000Z","msg":"唔夠料告夾硬留records"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"放人只係做樣<br />\n遲下再捉再告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a1795e7a626a8ff5882e1e85d851f568e6b25d","tid":2346403,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e191e44e192afe40e572bcf189e8d441fc8ed069","tid":2346403,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:33:55.000Z","msg":"唔夠料告夾硬留records"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:36:18.000Z","msg":"張潔宜審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好事嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98fc6353c3602046ab4714655e3798cc76c85c3","tid":2346403,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6634b847277baa6035ca1268c1734865f24571","tid":2346403,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a69b9f50f2b75ef748b35a656a1c9aeadd2df50","tid":2346403,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as